sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
Utility methods for managing import set. Create, read, update and transform methods.

Inputs:

  • Operation - Operation.
  • Import Set Table - Import Set Table.
  • Import Set SysID - Import Set SysID.
  • SubFlow Name - SubFlow Name.
  • State - State.

Outputs:

  • Current Job Start Date - Current Job Start Date
  • Current Job Start Date Time - Current Job Start Date and Time
